Parts Services

Parts

Precision, reliability, and durability. Engineered for top performance

Genuine

Genuine parts are crafted to meet the exact specifications and standards of the vehicle brand. They ensure perfect fit, performance, and reliability. Typically available through authorized dealerships, these parts often come with a manufacturer warranty.

OEM

OEM parts offer the same quality and exact specifications as genuine parts but at a lower price point. These parts are a cost-effective alternative while maintaining high standards of performance and fit.

Replacement

Replacement parts are designed to restore your vehicle to its original condition. These parts are typically affordable and may be either OEM or compatible alternatives, offering a reliable solution to repairs and replacements without compromising on quality.

About

we started with a simple dream: to make a difference. Today, we continue to empower others to succeed and reach new heights.

  • 1983

    Our Humble Beginnings

    888 German Motors, Inc. was brainchild of the owner's and directors of Delodur Corporation, which started the business in 1983. Delodur Corporation is involved in the importation, wholesale and retail sales of BMW and Daimler Benz spare parts.

  • 2002

    Incorporated

    888 German Motors, Inc. was incorporated in 2002 as a service center for BMW and Daimler Benz passenger cars.

  • 2011

    Transition to Full Service
